# scalingMatrix

_scalingMatrix(aList)_

Answer the matrix corresponding to scaling along each coordinate axis

```
>>> [1 2 3].scalingMatrix
[1 0 0; 0 2 0; 0 0 3]
```

_scalingMatrix_ is an alias for _diagonalMatrix_.

* * *

See also: identityMatrix, diagonalMatrix

